result.title: Hello again :) Cheater/Glitcher Report #2
result.content:
Hello CF, if you read my first post, you know me ;) . Lets see who "cheated".

I was looking standings of Codeforces Round #396 (Div. 2), then I saw interesting one, someone unrated solved just last problem. S/he solved problem in 1:19, so s/he had time to solve at least problem A. I guess that it's someone's fake account to check s/his solution.

See our fake account's submission here. Good, he managed to solve problem E.

Lets see who cheated, I saw him on comments many times, he is Whistle! YES! You can see him on standings here.

Lets look their submissions, this is Whistle's submission, and this is fake accounts. Same solution, but place of functions, names of some variables, arrays changed. Same things in functions. Like cheaters in my last post...

Sorry for poor English.

How to improve your programming skills

DON'T CHEAT!!
